險狗不如去間好d嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed71c08547004cb3117611c86efa55d1720d1f0","tid":390091,"uid":2666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:18:51.000Z","msg":"做保險狗最好都係揀無底薪純佣 有底嘅多數有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 前保記"},{"pid":"c88d96a2aaac6151891c3ba372366894af9a0497","tid":390091,"uid":128010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人知中銀Wealth Management好唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e065878acef5a4ae20e9731108563bfc8f8f020","tid":390091,"uid":142653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3038dbfedef2a519462e12b29e8c8393df45376","tid":390091,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩gra 番緊永明 大專生plan<br />\n頭一個月包17000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽我manager講 走吾洗嘔番出黎</blockquote><br />\n吾你老母保險狗"},{"pid":"2407af2132c44b0f80533df79563296a8f27f741","tid":390091,"uid":61180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:26:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做保險狗最好都係揀無底薪純佣 有底嘅多數有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 前保記</blockquote><br />\n即係講到兩萬蚊一個月個d屬於上面巴打講如果跑唔夠數就要嘔返俾公司？<br />\n我有個fg fd諗住做，佢同我講過左probation加到4萬，我覺得有古惑但唔知點說服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e486dc953ad6735970b5f85144bc6c848ed82bd","tid":390091,"uid":2666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心唔明保險係點，有好多野法例要規定買保險，佢地唔洗搵個人黎處理既咩?一定要出去搵客sell,人壽，醫療保險?</blockquote><br />\nAgent一腳踢 搵客 sell客 售後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然有更多人收左你保費就消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於點解個個都sell客危疾 saving 因為呢啲單高佣<br />\n你當你年供一萬佢就可以代三千佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bbafd789a708273ecc6598736d22632f19d954","tid":390091,"uid":2666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做保險狗最好都係揀無底薪純佣 有底嘅多數有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 前保記</blockquote><br />\n即係講到兩萬蚊一個月個d屬於上面巴打講如果跑唔夠數就要嘔返俾公司？<br />\n我有個fg fd諗住做，佢同我講過左probation加到4萬，我覺得有古惑但唔知點說服佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽過有d case係 你唔到數嘅話間公司會當你借糧 你quit就追返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋除返開一個月搵4萬幾左右就會做到mdrt(你當top sales)<br />\n你個fd過probation就4萬荀到咁下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2563a0c2b15bfb45c48d3c7b866b48f5cd9165","tid":390091,"uid":142653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c30016b089ce199f04ed516283d8d0bb556d056a","tid":390091,"uid":2666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我係問好多法例規定要買既保險，比如勞工，房屋，消防等等，好多野都要買，佢哋唔使請個人返黎做既咩?</blockquote><br />\n其實Agent十項全能 有考2號gi牌就會識同埋賣到<br />\n但係呢啲保險冇肉食 通常唔係d客主動話買都唔會點理<br />\n當然都會有唔少同事係靠做gi開客源 始終法例規定總有人要買"},{"pid":"721975a5b8804c6020de6e14805195379cf5e7bf","tid":390091,"uid":142653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab22db1453e875cdc02ef605f69b9d83fed95c1a","tid":390091,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心唔明保險係點，有好多野法例要規定買保險，佢地唔洗搵個人黎處理既咩?一定要出去搵客sell,人壽，醫療保險?</blockquote><br />\nAgent一腳踢 搵客 sell客 售後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然有更多人收左你保費就消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於點解個個都sell客危疾 saving 因為呢啲單高佣<br />\n你當你年供一萬佢就可以代三千佣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係問好多法例規定要買既保險，比如勞工，房屋，消防等等，好多野都要買，佢哋唔使請個人返黎做既咩?</blockquote><br />\n果啲係財產責任險，屬於一般保險業務，Life狗識條春咩"}]}